bad Metropolitan Region''' is the metropolitan area covered by the city of [[Hyderabad]] in the Indian state of [[Telangana]]. The entire region is spread over the districts of [[Hyderabad District, India|Hyderabad District]], [[Medchal district|Medchal]], [[Ranga Reddy district|Ranga Reddy]], [[Sangareddy district|Sangareddy]], [[Medak district|Medak]], [[Siddipet district|Siddipet]] and [[Yadadri Bhuvanagiri district|Yadadri Bhuvanagiri]]. Under the jurisdiction of [[Hyderabad Metropolitan Development Authority]], it covers an area of {{convert|7257|sqkm|abbr=on}} and has a population of 10.58 million people.<ref name=pop/>\n[[File:HMDA Jurisdiction Map.jpg|thumb|Metropolitan Area |272px]]\n\n== Jurisdiction ==\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! S.No !! District !! Mandals / Tehsil !! Total Mandals\n|-\n|1\n| [[Hyderabad District, India|Hyderabad district]]\n| Complete district\n| 16\n|-\n|2\n| [[Medchal district]] || Complete district - [[Ghatkesar]], [[Shameerpet]], [[Medchal]], [[Uppal, Shamshabad mandal|Uppal]], [[Keesara]], [[Quthubullapur]], Medipally, Bachupally, Dundigal, Kapra, Balanagar, Kukatpally, Malkajgiri, Alwal\n| 14\n|-\n|3\n| [[Ranga Reddy district]]\n| [[Chevella]], [[Hayathnagar]], [[Ibrahimpatnam, Ranga Reddy district|Ibrahimpatnam]], [[Kandukur]], [[Maheshwaram]], [[Manchal]], [[Moinabad, Rangareddy district|Moinabad]], [[Rajendranagar]], [[Saroornagar]], [[Shahbad]], [[Shamshabad]], [[Shankerpally]], [[Yacharam]], Abdullapurmet, [[Balapur, Ranga Reddy district|Balapur]], [[Farooqnagar]], [[Gandipet]], [[Kothur]], Nandigama, [[Serilingampally]]\n| 20\n|-\n|4\n| [[Sangareddy district]] || [[Patancheru]], [[Ramachandrapuram, Medak|Ramachandrapuram]], [[Sangareddy]], Ameenpur, Gummadidala, Jinnaram, Kandi, Hathnoor\n| 8\n|-\n|5\n| [[Medak district]] || Manoharabad, Narsapur, Shivampet, Tupran\n| 4\n|-\n|6\n| [[Siddipet district]]\n| [[Markook, Telangana|Markook]], [[Mulug, Siddipet district|Mulugu]] and Wargal\n| 3\n|-\n|7\n| [[Yadadri Bhuvanagiri